	(31,'I easily miss the final voice notification when I am really concentrated, which means I don\'t stop the pomodoro when I should. This is probably because all voice notification sound similar, and thus the brain filters them out when I am concentrated. Note that I don\'t use the tick-tack sound.\r\n\r\nMy suggestion is to add a sound at the end of the pomodoro (e.g. a gong sound) in addition to the \"Time \'s up\".',0,0,1,56,'2011-04-15 06:21:40','2011-04-15 06:21:40','<code class=\'debug_dump\'>{\"SERVER_SOFTWARE\"=>\"Apache/2.2.3 (CentOS)\", \"SERVER_PROTOCOL\"=>\"HTTP/1.1\", \"SERVER_NAME\"=>\"pomodorocrate.com\", \"SERVER_ADMIN\"=>\"tech@easymedia.ro\", \"SERVER_ADDR\"=>\"195.216.222.67\", \"SERVER_PORT\"=>\"80\", \"REMOTE_ADDR\"=>\"194.197.79.18\", \"REMOTE_PORT\"=>\"42065\", \"REQUEST_METHOD\"=>\"GET\", \"QUERY_STRING\"=>\"\", \"DOCUMENT_ROOT\"=>\"/var/www/vhosts/pomodorocrate.com/rails/pomodorocrate/current/public/\", \"REQUEST_URI\"=>\"/contact_requests/new\", \"SCRIPT_NAME\"=>\"\", \"PATH_INFO\"=>\"/contact_requests/new\", \"HTTP_HOST\"=>\"pomodorocrate.com\", \"HTTP_USER_AGENT\"=>\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 5.1; rv:2.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/4.0\", \"HTTP_ACCEPT\"=>\"text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8\", \"HTTP_ACCEPT_LANGUAGE\"=>\"en-gb,en;q=0.5\", \"HTTP_ACCEPT_ENCODING\"=>\"gzip, deflate\", \"HTTP_ACCEPT_CHARSET\"=>\"ISO-8859-1,utf-8;q=0.7,*;q=0.7\", \"HTTP_REFERER\"=>\"http://pomodorocrate.com/todotodays\", \"HTTP_COOKIE\"=>\"__utma=193383474.984207670.1300778802.1302787522.1302845719.57; __utmz=193383474.1300778802.1.1.utmcsr=twitter.com|utmccn=(referral)|utmcmd=referral|utmcct=/; remember_token=BAhbB2k9IkUzMzA4NWFlNDJkNTAzZDM3MmQyZjIxNTc5YWY0ZWQ1Zjg2NDlkODM4MWYzMzU3MjdhYjY1YjEwMTBkZmFjMGI1--f9febfd7ab388e5e62e4823331a7169db80a8db2; _ketchup_session=BAh7B0kiD3Nlc3Npb25faWQGOgZFRiIlYzZhZjAxMTkwZDM0NDIyMjdlNmVmZmUwYmU4MGUwMDNJIhBfY3NyZl90b2tlbgY7AEZJIjFoT05MT29MazI4bXdYcGMxQjRDemRrb09JODA4LzZVcTVGWU1iN2RHOUxjPQY7AEY%3D--d